PLACE potatoes, onion, egg product, flour and salt into blender container; cover. Blend until smooth. Add breakfast patty pieces; cover. Blend an additional 5 to 10 seconds. HEAT 1 tsp. of the oil in nonstick skillet on medium heat. Add potato mixture to hot skillet to form 8 pancakes, using 1/4 cup of the potato mixture for each pancake. COOK 3 minutes on each side or until golden brown on both sides, adding remaining oil as necessary.